    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive example of the A80 chassis. This collector-grade vehicle features the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six with its original sequential twin-turbocharger setup, delivering linear power through the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is absolute, retaining the factory Torsen limited-slip differential and OEM Bilstein-tuned suspension for precise handling dynamics. All VIN stickers are present on original panels, confirming a no-accident history. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, and the engine bay remains in showroom configuration with no aftermarket modifications. This is a rare, investment-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
