    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a true 'time capsule' vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The Deep Obsidian Pearl paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium Nappa leather seats remain supple and firm with no bolster wear, and the interior still retains its original 'new car' scent. Every tech feature, from the high-resolution navigation to the 12-speaker premium audio system, operates with precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It has been maintained exclusively by the dealership, and I have a comprehensive binder of every service record since mile one. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion. This sale includes both original master keys, all factory manuals, and the unused original floor mats. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
